translation: Proceed to the next mission?{#Name=" "}
source: Proceed to the next mission?{#Name=" "}

translation: みんなで一つの場所に集まるデモ{#Name=" "}
source: みんなで一つの場所に集まるデモ{#Name=" "}

translation: Could it BE any more damp around here?{LF}Even my sweat is sweaty.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Could it BE any more damp around here?{LF}Even my sweat is sweaty.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Urrrgh...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Urrrgh...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: I know, right? This place blows chunks.{#Name="Dito"}
source: I know, right? This place blows chunks.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Yes, but the discomfort is somehow...exhilarating...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Yes, but the discomfort is somehow...exhilarating...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Yeah, whatever, freak.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Yeah, whatever, freak.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I vote we ditch this place ASAP.{#Name="Dito"}
source: I vote we ditch this place ASAP.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Decadus. Gimme some cloth, will ya?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Decadus. Gimme some cloth, will ya?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Are you hurt, my lady?{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Are you hurt, my lady?{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: No, this stupid forest made my period come early.{#Name="Zero"}
source: No, this stupid forest made my period come early.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Nnngh...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Nnngh...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: ...Dito's right. You are a freak.{#Name="Zero"}
source: ...Dito's right. You are a freak.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: H-Here, my lady. Have all the cloth you want.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: H-Here, my lady. Have all the cloth you want.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Oh ho! Well, isn't this strange?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho! Well, isn't this strange?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: The forest up ahead used to be far more lush{LF}and verdant than this.{#Name="Octa"}
source: The forest up ahead used to be far more lush{LF}and verdant than this.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Something has happened since last I visited.{LF}I can feel it!{#Name="Octa"}
source: Something has happened since last I visited.{LF}I can feel it!{#Name="Octa"}

translation: You can "feel" it? Goodness, what a load of{LF}superstitious nonsense.{#Name="Cent"}
source: You can "feel" it? Goodness, what a load of{LF}superstitious nonsense.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I, of course, reject such mystic foolishness{LF}in favor of science.{#Name="Cent"}
source: I, of course, reject such mystic foolishness{LF}in favor of science.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Proof! Theories! Experimentation!{LF}This is the way of the world!{#Name="Cent"}
source: Proof! Theories! Experimentation!{LF}This is the way of the world!{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Buuut I probably shouldn't expect you Neanderthals{LF}to understand any of that.{#Name="Cent"}
source: Buuut I probably shouldn't expect you Neanderthals{LF}to understand any of that.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Cram it, professor.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Cram it, professor.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: いいから、黙れ{#Name="ディト"}
source: いいから、黙れ{#Name="ディト"}

translation: Lady Zero, if I may?{LF}We should avoid mingling in this fog for long.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Lady Zero, if I may?{LF}We should avoid mingling in this fog for long.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Three's inside this forest, right?{LF}She's here, isn't she?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Three's inside this forest, right?{LF}She's here, isn't she?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You seem awfully pleased about that.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You seem awfully pleased about that.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I'm just excited to meet one of your sisters!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm just excited to meet one of your sisters!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Well, I'm excited to kill her.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Well, I'm excited to kill her.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Aw, come on!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Aw, come on!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I just hope we get to eat before fighting.{LF}I'm useless on an empty tummy!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I just hope we get to eat before fighting.{LF}I'm useless on an empty tummy!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Hey, Cent. What do you know about Two?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Hey, Cent. What do you know about Two?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Two? Two, Two, Two...{LF}Yeah, sorry. Don't know her.{#Name="Cent"}
source: Two? Two, Two, Two...{LF}Yeah, sorry. Don't know her.{#Name="Cent"}

translation: You mean you...forgot her?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You mean you...forgot her?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: How can I forget a person I've never met?{#Name="Cent"}
source: How can I forget a person I've never met?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I'm pretty sure I'd remember a silly name like "Two."{#Name="Cent"}
source: I'm pretty sure I'd remember a silly name like "Two."{#Name="Cent"}

translation: All right, guys. Time to go.{#Name="Zero"}
source: All right, guys. Time to go.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You want me to go butt roll ahead, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: You want me to go butt roll ahead, Zero?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It's "patrol," dummy! Not "butt roll!"{#Name="Zero"}
source: It's "patrol," dummy! Not "butt roll!"{#Name="Zero"}

translation: That's what I said! That's totally what I said!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: That's what I said! That's totally what I said!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You know, I keep waiting for him to get smarter,{LF}but it's just not happening.{#Name="Dito"}
source: You know, I keep waiting for him to get smarter,{LF}but it's just not happening.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: How 'bout it, Cent? Wanna add some biting wit{LF}to the situation?{#Name="Dito"}
source: How 'bout it, Cent? Wanna add some biting wit{LF}to the situation?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: ...Aw, come on. Gimme something. Anything! {#Name="Dito"}
source: ...Aw, come on. Gimme something. Anything! {#Name="Dito"}

translation: Hmm? ...What?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Hmm? ...What?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Oh, so NOW you decide to be normal?{LF}Pffft. Forget it. You're useless.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Oh, so NOW you decide to be normal?{LF}Pffft. Forget it. You're useless.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I just...can't stop thinking about this Two person...{#Name="Cent"}
source: I just...can't stop thinking about this Two person...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Time doesn't always flow in a single direction.{#Name="Accord"}
source: Time doesn't always flow in a single direction.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: Divergence: Branch B{#Name="Accord"}
source: Divergence: Branch B{#Name="Accord"}

translation: In the flow of post-Cataclysm history,{#Name="Accord"}
source: In the flow of post-Cataclysm history,{#Name="Accord"}

translation: if a unique set of conditions known as "singularities" come together,{#Name="Accord"}
source: if a unique set of conditions known as "singularities" come together,{#Name="Accord"}

translation: splits occur in time, resulting in the multiple-world divergence phenomenon.{#Name="Accord"}
source: splits occur in time, resulting in the multiple-world divergence phenomenon.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: It is now April the 1st, 1000 A.D.,{#Name="Accord"}
source: It is now April the 1st, 1000 A.D.,{#Name="Accord"}

translation: 28 days since the singularity known as Zero resumed activity.{#Name="Accord"}
source: 28 days since the singularity known as Zero resumed activity.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: The first anomaly occurred when Zero encountered the old man known as Octa...{#Name="Accord"}
source: The first anomaly occurred when Zero encountered the old man known as Octa...{#Name="Accord"}

translation: And the forest they were expected to enter manifested in a different form...{#Name="Accord"}
source: And the forest they were expected to enter manifested in a different form...{#Name="Accord"}

translation: M3210_E0020_QV: Begin Recording{#Name="Accord"}
source: M3210_E0020_QV: Begin Recording{#Name="Accord"}
